  • Constructor Details

    • Menu

      public Menu()
      Default constructor for the Menu class. This constructor initializes the properties of the Menu object with default values. It creates new instances of SimpleIntegerProperty, SimpleStringProperty, SimpleDoubleProperty, and SimpleBooleanProperty for menu_ID, menu_name, extra_cost, and active respectively.
